high_descs: Turn right, move to the table, not near the chair.
Pick up the apple that is on the right, between two cups.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the stove.
Put the apple into the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the apple in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Move to the  table to the right of you
Pick up a apple from the table
Move to the stove to the right of you around the counter
Heat the apple in the microwave and pick it up after closing the door
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Place the apple inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and turn left to face the white table.
Pick the apple up from the table.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the stove.
Put the apple in the microwave above the stove, shut the door, open the door and take the apple out and then shut the door.
Go to the right face the fridge and shut the door.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple in the fridge.
